Neovim checklist:
- Initialize Neovim plugins:
  - Install fzf-lua dependencies:
    - fzf:
      - [MacOS] `brew install fzf`
    - fd:
      - [MacOS] `brew install fd`
    - ripgrep:
      - [MacOS] `brew install ripgrep`
- Install LSP servers:
  - Lua:
    - [MacOS] `brew install lua-language-server`
  - Ruby:
    - [MacOS] TODO
  - Rust:
    - [MacOS] `brew install rust-analyzer`
